msgstr "``\"delta\"`` 显示自上次统计日志消息以来一些数字统计有多大变化。"

#: ../../../topics/extensions.rst:397
msgid ""
"The :setting:`PERIODIC_LOG_DELTA` setting determines the target stats. They "
"must have ``int`` or ``float`` values."
msgstr ""

